"assertIsNot` take two values and check whether the two values evaluate to "
"the same object or not. (Added by Michael Foord; :issue:`2578`.)"
msgstr ""
":meth:`~unittest.TestCase.assertIs` e :meth:`~unittest.TestCase.assertIsNot` "
